These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
House: farmhouse, ranch-style, townhouse, cape-cod
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an odd position##4
 2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 3. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person who's sport is cycling is not the cape-cod house##6
 5. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
 6. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 7. the person who's sport is skiing is not to the left of the ranch-style house##8
 8. the ranch-style house is not the person who's sport is volleyball##6
 9. the farmhouse house is not the person who's hobby is writing##6
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who's hobby is writing##1
11. the ranch-style house is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8
12. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
13. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##8
14. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| House    | farmhouse         | cape-cod     | townhouse     | ranch-style         |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | writing    | sudoku     | magic-tricks |
| Sport   | cycling       | ice-hockey | volleyball | skiing       |

