.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, balloon-flower, azalea, rose
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, folk, jazz, pop
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, colombian, german, thai
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the fan of pop##1
 2. the colombian is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
 3. the fan of pop is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsballoon-flower is not to the right of the colombian##8
 6. the german is not to the right of the person who growsrose##8
 7. the fan of jazz is somewhere to the left of the person who growsrose##5
 8. the thai is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5
 9. the chinese is on the left of the german##1
10. the person who growsrose is the german##1
11. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Flower   | amaryllis   | rose | balloon-flower    | azalea |
| Music-Genre   | jazz    | folk     | dubstep   | pop     |
| Nationality   | chinese | german   | colombian | thai    |

