.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
There 4 different types of food: orange, eggplant, peas, corn
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, sports, western
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, lacrosse, snowboarding
 1. the person eating orange is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is basketball##5
 2. the person eating eggplant is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating corn is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
 5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 6. the person watching western movies is not the person eating peas##6
 7. the person eating orange is not the person who's sport is lacrosse##6
 8. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is not to the right of the person eating orange##8
10. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person eating peas##1
11. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food         | peas       | orange | eggplant  | corn    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports       | western    | scientific | fantasy    |
| Sport         | snowboarding | baseball   | lacrosse   | basketball |

