3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
4. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##8
5. the owner of the hamster is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
6. the owner of the turtle is not to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##8
7. the owner of the hamster is the fan of jazz##1
8. the owner of the hamster is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person drinking fanta##7
9. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the fan of rock##1

